Html:
Add the following resource to your App.xaml, it will remove the underline from all hyperlink instances in your app.<br />
<pre><code>&lt;Style TargetType=&quot;{x:Type Hyperlink}&quot; BasedOn=&quot;{StaticResource {x:Type Hyperlink}}&gt;
  &lt;Setter Property=&quot;TextDecorations&quot; Value=&quot;None&quot;/&gt;
&lt;/Style&gt;</code></pre>
